Tottenham Signs Winger Gareth Bale to New 4 1/2 Contract Until 2015

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-03-19T20:16:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-19/tottenham-signs-winger-gareth-bales-to-new-4-1-2-contract-until-2015.html
Tottenham winger Gareth Bale signed
a new 4 1/2-year contract until 2015, the Premier League club
said on its website.  Bale, 21, has helped Tottenham reach the Champions League
quarterfinals in its debut in the competition. The Wales
international scored a hat trick against defending champion
Inter Milan during the group stage.  “Gareth is now one of the top left-sided players in the
world, he really is an amazing talent and can only get better,”
Spurs manager  Harry Redknapp  said. “He has got his whole future
ahead and he has everything going for him.”  Bale has scored 17 goals in 112 appearances since joining
Spurs from Southampton in 2007.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  